I think Anes was asking for clarification about the tile prefetch for the first visible scanline (y=0). Not rendering those scanlines is not an option because MMC2 and MMC4 auto-bankswitch after pattern table fetches in $0FD0-$0FEF and $1FD0-$1FEF.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sun Sep 18, 2005 1:34 pm</p><hr />
